Stress is real - and affects EVERYONE! 🤦‍♀️ Your favourite Cartoon Network stars share Safe Steps to feel better when life gets overwhelming and tough.

😴 Sleep tight (9 hours every night)
🥗 Eat right (Have fruits and vegetables with every meal)
🤸‍♀️ Get outside (Stretch it out!)
⏰ Take a break (15 minutes every time)
📝 Pen it down (Write your feelings in a diary)
🤳 Stay connected (Hang out with your friends)

Get more stress-management tips: ➡️ https://www.safestepskids.com/stress-busters
